This paper deals with the optimization of resource allocation in HetNets, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication protocols. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves probability distributions and optimization algorithms, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the trade-off between Spectral Efficiency (SE) and Energy Efficiency (EE), which are topics related to multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography (cs.CR).
